graph TB
    subgraph "RHOAI Operator (rhods-operator)"
        Controller[rhods-operator<br/>Main Controller]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Port 9443/HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Server<br/>Port 8080/HTTP]
        Renderer[Manifest Renderer<br/>Kustomize Engine]

        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes metrics| Metrics
        Controller -->|renders manifests| Renderer

        subgraph "Component Controllers"
            DashboardCtrl[Dashboard Controller]
            KServeCtrl[KServe Controller]
            PipelinesCtrl[Pipelines Controller]
            CodeFlareCtrl[CodeFlare Controller]
            RayCtrl[Ray Controller]
            KueueCtrl[Kueue Controller]
            ModelRegCtrl[Model Registry Controller]
            ModelMeshCtrl[ModelMesh Controller]
            TrustyAICtrl[TrustyAI Controller]
            TrainingCtrl[Training Controller]
            WorkbenchCtrl[Workbenches Controller]
            FeastCtrl[Feast Controller]
            LlamaStackCtrl[LlamaStack Controller]
            ModelControllerCtrl[Model Controller]
        end

        subgraph "Service Controllers"
            AuthCtrl[Auth Service Controller]
            MonitoringCtrl[Monitoring Service Controller]
            ServiceMeshCtrl[ServiceMesh Controller]
            SecretCtrl[Secret Generation Controller]
            CertCtrl[Certificate Management Controller]
        end

        subgraph "Platform Controllers"
            FeatureTracker[Feature Tracker Controller]
            HardwareProfile[Hardware Profile Manager]
        end

        Controller -->|manages| DashboardCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| KServeCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| PipelinesCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| CodeFlareCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| AuthCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| MonitoringCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| ServiceMeshCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| FeatureTracker
        Controller -->|manages| HardwareProfile
    end

    User[Admin/GitOps] -->|creates| DSCCR[DataScienceCluster CR]
    User -->|creates| DSCICR[DSCInitialization CR]

    DSCCR -->|watched by| Controller
    DSCICR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| ComponentCRs[Component CRs:<br/>Dashboard, KServe,<br/>Pipelines, etc.]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceCRs[Service CRs:<br/>Auth, Monitoring,<br/>ServiceMesh]
    Controller -->|creates| FeatureTrackerCR[FeatureTracker CR]
    Controller -->|creates| HardwareProfileCR[HardwareProfile CR]

    Renderer -->|deploys 220+ manifests| ComponentNamespaces[Component Namespaces]

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/HTTPS]
        PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
        IstioOp[Service Mesh Operator]
        ServerlessOp[Serverless Operator]
        AuthorinoOp[Authorino Operator]
        CertManager[cert-manager]
    end

    Controller -->|REST API| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|deploys ServiceMonitors| PrometheusOp
    Controller -->|creates ServiceMeshMembers| IstioOp
    Controller -->|manages KnativeServing| ServerlessOp
    Controller -->|creates AuthConfigs| AuthorinoOp

    subgraph "Deployed Components"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        KServe[KServe Controller]
        DSP[Data Science Pipelines]
        CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Controller]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service]
    end

    Renderer -->|deploys| Dashboard
    Renderer -->|deploys| KServe
    Renderer -->|deploys| DSP
    Renderer -->|deploys| CodeFlare
    Renderer -->|deploys| ModelMesh
    Renderer -->|deploys| ModelRegistry
    Renderer -->|deploys| TrustyAI

